            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EGiving%20is%20a%20privilege%20that%20God%20allows%20us%20so%20that%20we%20may%20participate%20in%20His%20blessing.%20%22For%20God%20so%20loved%20the%20world%20that%20he%20gave%20his%20only%20Son%2C%20so%20that%20everyone%20who%20believes%20in%20him%20will%20not%20perish%20but%20have%20eternal%20life%22%20(John%203%3A16).%20When%20we%20%22so%20love%2C%22%20we%20also%20will%20%22give.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPaul%20challenged%20the%20Corinthians%20to%20prove%20the%20sincerity%20of%20their%20love%20(2%20Corinthians%208%3A8)%20with%20a%20willingness%20to%20give%20a%20missionary%20offering%20to%20the%20poor%20saints%20at%20Jerusalem.%20By%20so%20doing%2C%20they%20literally%20would%20be%20%22casting%20their%20bread%20upon%20the%20waters%2C%22%20sending%20their%20resources%20across%20the%20Mediterranean%20to%20a%20group%20of%20saints%20in%20desperate%20need.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhenever%20you%20purpose%20to%20give%2C%20the%20enemy%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20are%20wasting%20your%20money%20and%20throwing%20it%20away.%20He%20will%20point%20out%20to%20you%20all%20your%20own%20needs%20and%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20can't%20afford%20to%20give.%20In%20those%20times%2C%20you%20must%20remember%20that%20God's%20Word%20is%20true%20and%20that%20whatever%20you%20give%20will%20one%20day%20find%20its%20way%20back%20to%20you.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThose%20you%20provide%20for%20now%20out%20of%20your%20abundance%20may%20one%20day%20provide%20for%20you%20out%20of%20their%20abundance%20(2%20Corinthians%208%3A14).%20Even%20if%20you%20never%20see%20any%20reward%20here%20on%20earth%20for%20your%20generosity%2C%20you%20will%20reap%20in%20eternity%20the%20full%20return%20of%20what%20you%20have%20sown%20on%20earth.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20selfish%20will%20%22die%20%5Band%5D%20carry%20nothing%20with%20them.%20Their%20wealth%20will%20not%20follow%20them%20into%20the%20grave%22%20(Psalm%2049%3A17).%20But%20those%20who%20give%20will%20reap%20a%20sure%20reward.%20%20Start%20sowing%20generously%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20others%2C%20both%20here%20and%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20dividends%20are%20eternal!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
