            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEcclesiastes%2010%3A1-12%3A14%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_1%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEcclesiastes%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20dead%20flies%20cause%20even%20a%20bottle%20of%20perfume%20to%20stink%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20a%20little%20foolishness%20spoils%20great%20wisdom%20and%20honor.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_2%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20wise%20person%20chooses%20the%20right%20road%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ea%20fool%20takes%20the%20wrong%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_3%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20can%20identify%20fools%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ejust%20by%20the%20way%20they%20walk%20down%20the%20street!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_4%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20your%20boss%20is%20angry%20at%20you%2C%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20quit!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EA%20quiet%20spirit%20can%20overcome%20even%20great%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_5%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Ironies%20of%20Life%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan