%22poet2%22%3Eso%20sharpen%20the%20blade.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20the%20value%20of%20wisdom%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eit%20helps%20you%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_11%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20a%20snake%20bites%20before%20you%20charm%20it%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20the%20use%20of%20being%20a%20snake%20charmer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_12%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EWise%20words%20bring%20approval%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20fools%20are%20destroyed%20by%20their%20own%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_13%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EFools%20base%20their%20thoughts%20on%20foolish%20assumptions%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20their%20conclusions%20will%20be%20wicked%20madness%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_14%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Ethey%20chatter%20on%20and%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3ENo%20one%20really%20knows%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eno%20one%20can%20predict%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_10_15%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%2210%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EFools%20are%20so%20exhausted%20by%20a%20little%20work%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%